name: carcosa1
description:
"An inhabitant of Carcosa", a tribute to the King in Yellow short story collection and to all of the laborers in the field of eerie fiction that weren't HP Lovecraft. A special nod to August Derleth who was both a local and also did more for the curation of the weird and eerie as a literary form than HP Lovecraft's racist ass ever did..
